metadata.Author: Thomas Tyack
metadata.Comment:
This is the Sitecore Azure Search Spatial demo installation package.
Please install the Core package prior to installing this package. Available Here: https://github.com/Aceik/Sitecore-Azure-Search-Spatial/tree/master/lib/Package Documentation: https://github.com/Aceik/Sitecore-Azure-Search-Spatial/wiki/
Please note this demo is intended to be run on a Vanilla (clean/fresh) installation of Sitecore 8.2.5 or greater. Installing this package will change the homepage item and may override your data.
